      <title>橙子种植者期待转机。然后米尔顿来了。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/florida-orange-growers-were-set-for-a-turnaround-then-hurricane-milton-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风米尔顿席卷佛罗里达州后，佛罗里达州的橙子和一些柑橘树倒在地上，毫无生机，种植者们原本以为这个陷入困境的行业最糟糕的时期已经过去，但事实却让他们措手不及。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/florida-orange-growers-were-set-for-a-turnaround-then-hurricane-milton-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
